summary:
Lara Croft Default Body Changer for \"TOMB RAIDER 2013 by m0ckin9bird\" mod
This will help you to change the lara croft\'s default body to your custom body.
descriptionHtml:
[b]Introduction [/b]
Lara Croft Default Body Changer for \"TOMB RAIDER 2013 by m0ckin9bird\" mod
This will help you to change the lara croft\'s default body to your custom body.

[b]Download  [/b]
You can download this file from (third party URL)
http://www62.zippyshare.com/v/58096708/file.html
or you can even download it from here nexus. 

[b]Installation Instructions [/b]
Download and Extract to any location

[b]Usage Instructions [/b]
Read the Help Section on the tool

[b]Requirements [/b]
first you need this mod
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/33524

then you need a custom body mod like CBBE,UNPB etc..
if you are fine with UNP body then don\'t use this tool because the \"TOMB RAIDER 2013 by m0ckin9bird\" is already shipped with the UNP body in default. 

[b]NOTE. [/b]
I don\'t provide any files you have to manually download everything by yourself.
you need few mods to make this tool works and those are the mods that I have mentioned above under the Requirements section 

[b]Permission. [/b]
Share this tool with whoever you want, redistribution is also allowed. you don\'t need to ask my permission for that. you don\'t even need to mention my name when you share it (because it\'s already been mentioned in the about me section, Just don\'t try to remove it by reverse engineering)

[b]Author [/b]
Gryphex
